<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1756133-should-i-read-the-atlantis-gene-before">Should I read The Atlantis Gene before reading Pandemic or is Pandemic not part of the trilogy?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1756133'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F34811896-pandemic">like</a></span>

