<span id="freeTextContainer1347179582119998158">I loved, loved, loved the first 3/4 of this book.<br/>(sigh)<br/>The last quarter was quite complicated, overly complicated. The plot seemed a stretch, there were SCORES of coincidences that I still can&apos;t explain, and I just wanted it to be over. <br/>But that first 3/4 was excellent!<br/><br/>Note: Some language.</span>
  <span id="freeText1347179582119998158" style="display:none">I loved, loved, loved the first 3/4 of this book.<br />(sigh)<br />The last quarter was quite complicated, overly complicated. The plot seemed a stretch, there were SCORES of coincidences that I still can't explain, and I just wanted it to be over. <br />But that first 3/4 was excellent!<br /><br />Note: Some language.</span>
