<div id="review_2343397022" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2343397022" />
    <a title="Jen" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/11913659-jen"><img alt="Jen" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1450473254p2/11913659.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2343397022?book_show_action=true">Apr 02, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jen" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jen" href="/user/show/11913659-jen">Jen</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Audible Audio " href="/book/show/35583120-pandemic">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/11913659-jen?shelf=adult">adult</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/11913659-jen?shelf=audiobook">audiobook</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/11913659-jen?shelf=contemporary">contemporary</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/11913659-jen?shelf=sci-fi">sci-fi</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/11913659-jen?shelf=mystery">mystery</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2343397022" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer33628785498903709">I&apos;m a sucker for &quot;plague kills the world&quot; books and this was just what I was craving. Tons of adventure, engaging characters, a fast pace and a plague that kills the world! Couldn&apos;t ask for more from a good p/a. This one sped along and I just didn&apos;t want to put it down. <br/><br/>The narration by Eduardo Ballerini is spectacular. His command of accents is impressive.</span>
  <span id="freeText33628785498903709" style="display:none">I'm a sucker for "plague kills the world" books and this was just what I was craving. Tons of adventure, engaging characters, a fast pace and a plague that kills the world! Couldn't ask for more from a good p/a. This one sped along and I just didn't want to put it down. <br /><br />The narration by Eduardo Ballerini is spectacular. His command of accents is impressive.</span>
